<title>SRI LANKA: Sri Lanka's Marawila Hotels to launch IPO.</title>
<headline>Sri Lanka's Marawila Hotels to launch IPO.</headline>
<dateline>COLOMBO 1997-03-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sri Lanka's Marawila Resorts Ltd said in a statement on Monday it was planning to launch an initial public offer of 15.6 million shares at a par value of 10 rupees, the island's first this year.</p>
<p>The statement said the company had already raised part of its planned 300 million rupee capital through a private share placement.</p>
<p>The company said it had applied to the Colombo Stock Exchange for permission to list all its shares, including those already issued.</p>
<p>The issue opens on March 26.</p>
